      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates. Mechanically sound, the rod bearing service and throttle body actuators have been proactively addressed. Power is sent through the lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is dialed, and the subframe mounting points are intact. A driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
